Note on Facebook idb: sim-use links against XCFrameworks built from Meta's idb
and ships them in its release artifacts. The idb source is not vendored in this
repository — it is fetched and patched at build time (see patches/idb/) — so it
does not appear in the source-level scan, but it is a real dependency and is
attributed below.


